# Sentry File Structure Rules

**Filepaths:** `src/sentry/*/`, `tests/sentry/*/`

## Django App Organization

```
src/sentry/{app_name}/
├── models/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── {model_name}.py
├── endpoints/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── urls.py
│   ├── {endpoint_name}.py
│   └── serializers/
│       ├── __init__.py
│       └── {model_name}.py
├── migrations/
└── apps.py
```

## Test Structure
Test directories mirror the django app structure.

```
tests/sentry/{app_name}/
```


## Naming Conventions

- **Python files**: snake_case
- **Classes**: PascalCase
- **API responses**: camelCase
- **URLs**: kebab-case
- **Database fields**: snake_case
